            +b explicit read authorization is supported, from components to be released from
            +b active service and/or decommissioned."
        requirement_id "IEC 62443-4-2: CR 4.2"
        title "Information Persistence"
        description "This requirement addresses the need to ensure that sensitive information is not
            +b improperly exposed or accessible after it is no longer needed. It requires that
            +b systems and components securely handle the persistence of sensitive data,
            +b ensuring that information is appropriately retained or disposed of according to
            +b policy."
