                details "Ensures that data is disposed of in a manner that prevents unauthorized
                    +b recovery, using techniques such as data wiping or degaussing."
            {
                aspect "Access Control"
                details "Implements access controls to prevent unauthorized retrieval of sensitive
                    +b information during its retention period."
            {
